cu.explanation_en: Setting ASN.1 verbosity to an invalid enum value will cause configuration parsing errors and prevent the CU from starting properly.

du.explanation_en: Setting ASN.1 verbosity to an invalid enum value will cause configuration parsing errors and prevent the DU from starting properly.
du.explanation_zh: 將 ASN.1 詳細程度設定為無效的枚舉值將導致配置解析錯誤，並阻止 DU 正確啟動。
